469
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:20,520
Hurry up.

470
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:29,240
CHUAN N 97023

471
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,760
If we pull this off,

472
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,640
