494
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:20,160
Chuan N 97023. Silver van.

495
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:22,400
<i>Just passed the Wei Tunnel 9,</i>
<i>heading south.</i>

496
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,560
