- Dad!

526
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,200
- Dad, I'm here!
- Out!

527
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:19,520
Dad, I'm here!

528
00:40:20,720 --> 00:40:22,320
- Run him over.
- Dad!

529
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:24,960
- Help!
- Step on the gas!

530
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:26,880
- He's a cop.
- You chickened out?

531
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:27,880
All of you, out!

532
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:28,840
- Run him over!
- Dad!

533
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:29,800
Help!

534
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,840
Quick!

535
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,680
Dad! Dad!

536
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,160
- Get out!
- Help me!

537
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:46,400
Get out! Get out!

538
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:47,760
Move!

539
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:50,000
- Don't hit my dad!
- Move!

540
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:51,840
