541
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:53,880
Out of my way!

542
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,960
Don't hit my dad!

543
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:57,840
I won't forgive you!

544
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,880
- Step on it.
- Don't hit my dad!

545
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,360
Run him over!

546
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:10,360
Dad!

547
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,600
Dad!
